summary:
Graphic Designer currently based in The Netherlands.
Experience and previous work have taught me how to analyse briefs, find objectives and communicate to the target audience with the appropriate outcome.
My work can be diverse; and being flexible in both print and digital has allowed me to take part in a variety of projects, finding solutions for clients with a range of visual profiles.
For me, commitment to creativity is the key to an original result.
